<br>
What was a pisser was, the night before in the same camp I had 65 Druid Healer and I didnt die once! And rarely lost aggro (Wiz Bard Rogue in Group also). There was the occasional overburn or High Damage BS, but I always regained quickly. <br>
<br>
The Reason this happens is because there is so much talk about it, people automagically believe it to be the fix. They think, &quot;Oh, Warrior Lost aggro on that one, cant be my fault, lets get a Paladin!&quot;<br>
<br>
Dont get me wrong, I know there are issues with Taunt that should be looked at, but remember, when some uninformed Grape Vine Listening Idiot gives you that line, dont feel bad... Its Not your fault they are Moron's!<br>
<br>
Valhalan Trueblade<br>
